<collectingCountry id="F31E7642FFCDFFCCFB4CFD47E2E6FCF4" box="[1159,1243,752,781]" name="China" pageId="8" pageNumber="415">China</collectingCountry>
at the end of the Miocene. The monophyly of 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D51FFCDFFCCFD25FC8DE51AFCA2" box="[750,807,826,859]" class="Mammalia" family="Cervidae" genus="Axis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="8" pageNumber="415" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Axis</taxonomicName>
has been questioned repeatedly but the most recent genetic analyses have confirmed it. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
